Conclusion & Future Work
This extended Library Management System shows that even a few beginner-level C concepts can easily be scaled into a more realistic solution.
 Data persistence, multiple search strategies, statistics, and borrower tracking were introduced within this project.
While simple, it lays the foundation for more professional systems.

